m/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3578980/extras/8307d12eb00ae9ab74c54489860335c0.poster.avif?t=1769853786\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3578980/extras/8307d12eb00ae9ab74c54489860335c0.webm?t=1769853786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3578980/extras/8307d12eb00ae9ab74c54489860335c0.mp4?t=1769853786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>", "short_description": "You take the role of a Tentacle Monster contained as an anomaly in a research facility. As scientists, researchers, and guards go against you, will you be able to escape your containment through your tentacle lockers?", "supported_languages": "English", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3578980/4540477966b96a4bcb60d8da8fbb68830ddf30e3/header.jpg?t=1769853786", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3578980/463103944c8fbb67e74c094b672719df92142f9a/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1769853786", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3578980/463103944c8fbb67e74c094b672719df92142f9a/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1769853786", "website": "http://strangegirlstudios.com/", "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS *:</strong> Windows 7<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> x86_64 or ARMv8 (SSE4.2 required for 4.5)<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 4 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> GPU supporting OpenGL 3.3<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 2 GB available space</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Windows 10<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Modern quad-core processor (Intel i5/Ryzen 5)<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 8 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> Dedicated GPU supporting V